How to mod your game

1. Create a mods folder: Rooftops and Alleys > Content > Paks. And create a mod folder in there.

2. Join the Rooftops and Alleys official Discord Server

3. Go to community-mods channel, find the mod you want and download it.

4. Once downloaded, extract the file and place the files that are inside the folder (e.g. backpack_p.pak/.ucas/.utoc) into the RNA mods folder you created.

5. Launch your game and you sohuld have the mods.
